if.description:
Conditionally displays its contents based on the given expression.

Usage:

```
{if condition}
  ...
{elseif condition}
  ...
{else}
  ...
{/if}
```

switch.description:
Evaluates an expression and executes the matching `{case}` branch.

Usage:

```
{switch expression}
  {case value1}
    ...
  {case value2}
    ...
  {default}
    ...
{/switch}
```

timed.description:
Displays its contents after a specified delay.

Usage:

```
{timed delay}
  ...
  {next delay}
  ...
{/timed}
```
